<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink396">
<l>pulippoṟi vēṅkaip poṉṉiṇar koytuniṉ</l>
<l>katuppaya laṇiyu maḷavai paipayac</l>
<l>curattiṭai yayarcciyai yāṟuka maṭantai</l>
<l>kalkeḻu ciṟappi nammū</l>
<l>relvirun tākip pukuka nāmē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O girl! Let’s slowly take rest from the fatigue in the wilderness,</l>
<l>while [we] pluck golden clusters of Vēnkai flowers, </l>
<l>[resembling] spots on leopard, and adorn [your] hair. </l>
<l>Let’s enter our village, famous for its rocks,</l>
<l>after the midday feast! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
